      • getTypedAttributeValue

        public final <T> T getTypedAttributeValue(XMLAttributeDeclaration<T> attribute)
        Gets the typed value of the given attribute. Returns null if the attribute is not set, or if the value in the node could not be converted into an instance of T.

        NOTE: It is assumed that values that could not be converted to the expected type, e.g., a malformed integer, that the document is invalid w.r.t. the schema, and that violation would be reported by other means.
